{{Infobox newspaper | name = Ardealul | logo = | image = | caption = | type = | format = | owners = | founder = [[Onisifor Ghibu]] | publisher = | editor = | chiefeditor = [[Onisifor Ghibu]] | assoceditor = | maneditor = | newseditor = | managingeditordesign = | campuseditor = | campuschief = | opeditor = | sportseditor = | photoeditor = | staff = [[Ion Matei]], A. Gheorghiu, V. Cijevski, A. Murafa | foundation = October 1, 1917 | political = | language = [[Romanian language|Romanian]] | ceased publication = January 1918 (successor: [[România Nouă]]) | headquarters = [[Chişinău]] | circulation = | sister newspapers = | ISSN = | oclc = | website = }}
'''''Ardealul''''' ({{lang-en|Transylvania}}) was a weekly newspaper from [[Chişinău]], the [[Moldavian Democratic Republic|Moldavian Republic]], founded by [[Onisifor Ghibu]] in October 1917. Initially, the newspaper was published weekly, later appeared three times a week. After January 1918, its successor was the daily newspaper [[România Nouă]].<ref>[http://www.hasdeu.md/ro/ebibl/poslednij.pdf PRESA BASARABEANĂ de la începuturi pînă în anul 1957. Catalog] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120304035846/http://www.hasdeu.md/ro/ebibl/poslednij.pdf |date=2012-03-04 }}</ref>
